{"tid":1026453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"魔鬼山行山猝死男 為立法會秘書處保安員","createTime":"2019-02-18T06:31:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T08:42:13.000Z","uid":30647,"like":83,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d76b10b398c151693b575fcb0f769d53a6eb4452","tid":1026453,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T06:31:40.000Z","msg":"原來係立法會保安<br />\n---------<br />\n上周六油塘魔鬼山45歲姓陳行山男子不適送院，最終不治，立法會主席梁君彥今日透露，姓陳死者為立法會秘書處保安員，梁代表全體議員向死者家屬致深切慰問，並承諾協助家人度過難關。<br />\n<br />\n上周六(16日)正午12時23分，陳在油塘魔鬼山行山期間不適，感到胸口痛，報警求助。陳繼而暈倒昏迷，稍後由政府飛行服務隊直升機送到東區醫院搶救。但他送院時已陷昏迷，經搶救後不治。當日天氣炎熱，根據天文台資料，觀塘最高氣溫為27&deg;C。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190218/59272747\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190218%2F59272747&d=8lKb2kYWDOzPE5G8cc2TgLZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=784d5a03\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190218%2F59272747&h=2c7611d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190218/59272747</a>"},{"pid":"2fb1ef6f6c1496d6838dcef0b65c3612fe9e0097","tid":1026453,"uid":35930,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T06:33:32.000Z","msg":"咁好死嘅"},{"pid":"6fd910d5aedb4043cff9df536ccca5a2bf64317b","tid":1026453,"uid":72009,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T06:34:21.000Z","msg":"天意"},{"pid":"188b2d1f393e632af17266b732545fabbd87bc4e","tid":1026453,"uid":14918,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T06:35:31.000Z","msg":"正皮對抗負皮狗"},{"pid":"a55c7f9b92d278a7227ecff1dbd8566fbd592245","tid":1026453,"uid":163350,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T06:36:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cc98e990fe776ff93fa779ec4127202eb808efd4","tid":1026453,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20